        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 132905,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Una redirección es cuando un servidor web le dice a tu navegador que vaya a una página diferente.</p><p>Los redireccionamientos son fundamentales. Guían a los usuarios al contenido correcto cuando las páginas se mueven, se renombran o según condiciones específicas.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3",
            "id": 132878,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>En lugar de devolver una respuesta a través del objeto de respuesta, llamamos a <code>redirect</code> en él.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect();\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"56\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>res</code> seguido de <code>.</code> y finalmente <code>redirect</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy",
            "id": 132906,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Proporcionamos una nueva ruta a la que se debe redirigir la solicitud.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"56\" /><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>res</code> seguido de <code>.</code> y luego <code>redirect</code>, <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132908,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Respondemos con una nueva ruta y, como siempre, un código de estado.</p><p>El código de estado <code>302 Found</code> indica que el recurso solicitado ha sido movido temporalmente a la URL proporcionada en la respuesta.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"302\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"61\" /><option startIndex=\"62\" endIndex=\"74\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>302</code> seguido de <code>,</code> y finalmente <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy  Copy",
            "id": 132909,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>No tenemos que establecer explícitamente <code>302 Found</code> ya que se establece implícitamente si usamos <code>redirect</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"69\" /><option startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"56\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>res</code> seguido de <code>.</code> y luego <code>redirect</code>, <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132907,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Cuando el cliente recibe <code>302 Found</code> junto con una nueva URL, típicamente, redirigirá llamando al endpoint proporcionado.</p><p>Aquí, el cliente será redirigido de <code>\"/old-route\"</code> a <code>\"/new-route\"</code>, recibiendo un estado <code>200 OK</code> y un mensaje.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.status(\" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\").send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;You found me!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"97\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"/old-route\"</code> seguido de <code>\"/new-route\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4",
            "id": 132879,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Por el contrario, un redireccionamiento permanente <code>301 Moved Permanently</code> indica un cambio permanente en la ubicación del recurso.</p><p>Cambiemos nuestro redireccionamiento temporal anterior a uno permanente.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"301\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"302\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>301</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #5",
            "id": 132880,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Express también permite el enrutamiento basado en declaraciones condicionales. Publicar una nueva versión es fácil con redirecciones.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/:version&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (req.params.version == \" /><text value=\"&quot;1.0&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  res.send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Version 1.0&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" } \" /><text value=\"else\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/1.0&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"117\" endIndex=\"120\" /><option startIndex=\"120\" endIndex=\"121\" /><option startIndex=\"121\" endIndex=\"129\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>res</code> seguido de <code>.</code> y finalmente <code>redirect</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #4 - Copy",
            "id": 132910,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>También puedes usar redirecciones cuando trabajas con un router.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"router.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"router.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"301\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"6\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>router</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132912,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Redirigir de <code>\"/friends\"</code> a <code>\"/homies\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/friends&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"302\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/homies&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/homies&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.status(\" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\").send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;What's up?&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"85\" endIndex=\"94\" /><option startIndex=\"60\" endIndex=\"69\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;/friends&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"/friends\"</code> seguido de <code>\"/homies\"</code> y finalmente <code>\"/homies\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #15",
            "id": 132917,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cómo estableces manualmente el código de estado para una redirección en Express?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>res.redirect(301, \"/new-route\")</code></item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\"><code>res.redirect(\"/new-route\", 301)</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\"><code>res.redirect(301, \"/new-route\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #3 - Copy - Copy - Copy - Copy",
            "id": 132914,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Establece el código de estado para una redirección permanente.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/old-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"req, res\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"301\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/new-route&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"60\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"302\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>301</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Lesson #17",
            "id": 132919,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Crea una redirección temporal de <code>\"/store\"</code> a <code>\"/shop\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"app.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/store&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", (req, res) =&gt; {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  res.redirect(\" /><text value=\"302\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\", \" /><text value=\"&quot;/shop&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"app.get(\" /><text value=\"&quot;/shop&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\", (req, res) =&gt; {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" res.status(\" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\").send(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome to the shop!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"});\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"16\" /><option startIndex=\"49\" endIndex=\"52\" /><option startIndex=\"54\" endIndex=\"61\" /><option startIndex=\"77\" endIndex=\"84\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;/store&quot;\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"301\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"/store\"</code> seguido de <code>302</code> y luego <code>\"/shop\"</code>, <code>\"/shop\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          }
        ]
      }
